snippet.title: Imagine Lifetimes - Early Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Imagine Lifetimes is a satirical simulation game about the meaning of life.

The first (early access) build was released on August 31st 2019 on GameJolt.
Link: https://gamejolt.com/games/imaginelifetimes/348701

Features:
- Dreadfully lighthearted entertainment
- The true meaning of life
- An existential crisis

Let me know what you believe the meaning of life is, your feedback is invaluable!
E-mail: frycandle@gmail.com
